# Copy to .env.local and fill in. Both .env and .env.local are gitignored.
#
# Linear is OPTIONAL. The ONLY value you may need here is your personal API key.
# Without it, the Linear hooks skip cleanly (no errors). The shared, non-secret
# team + workflow-state IDs are already committed in .claude/linear.shared.env —
# do NOT duplicate them here.
#
# Personal Linear API key — create at: https://linear.app/settings/api
LINEAR_API_KEY=lin_api_...
